_Thenn\" title=\"Magnar of Thenn\">Magnar of Thenn</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Former <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a> <sup>(King of Winter)</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"King of the First Men\">King of the First Men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Marsh_King\" title=\"Marsh King\">Marsh King</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Red King</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Former <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_Rivers\" title=\"King of the Isles and the Rivers\">King of the Isles and the Rivers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rock_king\" title=\"Rock king\">Rock king</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Salt_king\" title=\"Salt king\">Salt king</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Former <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-